$ NastAero VM3: Simply-Supported Plate Under Uniform Pressure
$ Reference: Timoshenko - Theory of Plates and Shells
$ 8x8 CQUAD4 mesh, a=b=1.0m, t=0.01m, E=200GPa, nu=0.3
$ Uniform pressure p=1000 Pa (applied as nodal forces)
$ Analytical center deflection:
$ w_max = alpha*p*a^4/D where alpha=0.00406 for a/b=1
$ D = E*t^3/(12*(1-nu^2)) = 200e9*1e-6/(12*0.91) = 18315.02 N-m
$ w_max = 0.00406*1000*1.0/18315.02 = 2.216e-4 m
$
SOL 101
CEND
TITLE = VM3 - SIMPLY SUPPORTED PLATE UNDER PRESSURE
SPC = 1
LOAD = 1
DISPLACEMENT(PRINT) = ALL
BEGIN BULK
