$ Uniform pressure 1000 Pa as nodal forces
$ Interior nodes: full tributary area = 0.125*0.125 = 0.015625 m^2
$ Edge nodes: half area = 0.0078125 m^2
$ Corner nodes: quarter area = 0.00390625 m^2
$ Force = pressure * area (in -Z direction... but SS plate -> +Z for gravity convention)
$ Actually applying as downward force (-Z) at each node
$ Interior nodes (49 nodes): F = 1000 * 0.015625 = 15.625 N
$ Edge interior (28 nodes): F = 1000 * 0.0078125 = 7.8125 N
$ Corner nodes (4 nodes): F = 1000 * 0.00390625 = 3.90625 N
$
